title: The Lord is my Shepherd I shall not want, He maketh me to lie down In green pastures, Leave, O leave, O leave me not alone. Leave O, Leave, O leave me not alone, Leave, O leave, O leave me not alone, He's my Shepherd I shall not want.
lyrics: The Lord is my Shepherd I shall not want, He maketh me to lie down In green pastures, Leave, O leave, O leave me not alone. Leave O, Leave, O leave me not alone, Leave, O leave, O leave me not alone, He's my Shepherd I shall not want.
